OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1781599695
OL,3,CTwo-year-old boy seriously injured
OL,4,Cafter car crashes into nursery
OL,5,Cplayground
OL,7,FA two-year-old boy has been seriously
OL,8,Finjured and another two children hurt
OL,9,Fafter a car crashed into a nursery
OL,10,Fplayground.
OL,12,FEmergency services were called to the
OL,13,Fincident on Vale Road, in the Whitby
OL,14,Farea of Ellesmere Port, Cheshire, at
OL,15,Faround 9.54am.
OL,17,FPartou Sunny Days Nursery and Pre-
OL,18,Fschool confirmed they were "dealing
OL,19,Fwith an incident".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
