PN,36502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1781599695
OL,3,CTwo-year-old boy seriously injured
OL,4,Cafter car crashes into nursery
OL,5,Cplayground
OL,7,FOfficers attended the scene alongside
OL,8,FNorth West Ambulance Service, where a
OL,9,Fcar had driven through a fence and
OL,10,Finto the playground area of the
OL,11,Fnursery.
OL,13,FA two-year-old boy is reported to have
OL,14,Fsuffered "serious injuries" and has
OL,15,Fbeen taken to hospital, while two
OL,16,Fother children sustained minor
OL,17,Finjuries.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
