OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,366,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1781599695
OL,3,CTwo-year-old boy seriously injured
OL,4,Cafter car crashes into nursery
OL,5,Cplayground
OL,7,FWitnesses reported seeing two
OL,8,Fambulances, an air ambulance, a fire
OL,9,Fengine and four police vehicles,
OL,10,Fincluding an armed response vehicle at
OL,11,Fthe scene.
OL,13,FA 63-year-old woman has been arrested
OL,14,Fon suspicion of causing serious injury
OL,15,Fby dangerous driving.
OL,17,FCheshire Police said: "At around
OL,18,F9.54am on Monday 15 June, officers
OL,19,Fresponded to reports of a collision at
OL,20,Fa nursery school on Vale Road in the
OL,21,FWhitby area of the town.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,366,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1781599695
OL,3,CTwo-year-old boy seriously injured
OL,4,Cafter car crashes into nursery
OL,5,Cplayground
OL,7,F"Officers attended the scene alongside
OL,8,Fcolleagues from the North West
OL,9,FAmbulance Service and found that a car
OL,10,Fhad driven through a fence and into
OL,11,Fthe playground area of the nursery.
OL,13,F"A two-year-old boy has sustained what
OL,14,Fare thought to be serious injuries and
OL,15,Fhas been taken to hospital for further
OL,16,Ftreatment. The child's next of kin
OL,17,Fhave been made aware.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,366,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1781599695
OL,3,CTwo-year-old boy seriously injured
OL,4,Cafter car crashes into nursery
OL,5,Cplayground
OL,7,F"Two other children sustained minor
OL,8,Finjuries following the incident.
OL,9,FOfficers are currently on scene and
OL,10,Fare conducting a number of enquiries
OL,11,Fto fully establish the circumstances
OL,12,Fof what is believed to be an isolated
OL,13,Fincident."
OL,15,FLocal MP Justin Madders said he was
OL,16,F"deeply saddened" to hear about the
OL,17,Fincident, adding, "My thoughts are
OL,18,Fwith the young child who was seriously
OL,19,Finjured, their family, the other
OL,20,Fchildren and everyone affected."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/5
